title: 10/04/21 DPS Hour 1 Peter King
itunes:title: 10/04/21 DPS Hour 1 Peter King
description:
In this hour of The Dan Patrick Show, it's reaction time to a buffet of sports results--from the NFL to college football to MLB playoff positioning. Plus, Peter King of "Football Morning In America" and NBCSports.com offers his opinions from Sunday's NFL results.
